================================================================================
What does this tell us?
  - "fastpass%" = boxes where lb_fast >= target (cheap bounds even attempted)
  - "ANY_cheap%" = boxes that pass the cheap rigor tier
  - The diff (fastpass - ANY_cheap) = boxes that lb_fast says yes but rigor refuses
  - If d=30 has lower fastpass% at moderate hw, the CHEAP tier is the binder
